OL,3,CInquest hears farm worker's payments
OL,4,Cwere delayed before death
OL,6,FThe inquest of a Filipino farm worker
OL,7,Fand father of three who died in Jersey
OL,8,Frevealed he knocked on the door of his
OL,9,Fneighbour's home the day before his
OL,10,Fdeath, asking for money and food.
OL,12,FGeorge Michael Monte De Ramos
OL,13,FCastrudes, 37, died in January 2025
OL,14,Ffrom hypoxic brain injury caused by
OL,15,Fcarbon monoxide poisoning at his
OL,16,Faccommodation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
