OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772110991
OL,3,CInquest hears farm worker's payments
OL,4,Cwere delayed before death
OL,6,FMr Castrudes worked and lived on a
OL,7,Ffarm and started a makeshift firepit
OL,8,Fin a washing machine drum in his
OL,9,Fportable cabin whilst temperatures
OL,10,Fwere below freezing.
OL,12,FMr Castrudes moved to the island from
OL,13,Fthe Philippines and had been living
OL,14,Fand working on the La Valette
OL,15,FNurseries Ltd site in Grouville for
OL,16,Fthree years, which is run by the Blake
OL,17,Ffamily.
OL,19,FGeorge was described by his sister,
OL,20,FGrace, as a father "dreaming of a
OL,21,Fbrighter future for his children."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772110991
OL,3,CInquest hears farm worker's payments
OL,4,Cwere delayed before death
OL,6,FThe inquest heard that George had
OL,7,Fexperience delays in his payments.
OL,9,FHe explained to his employer, Nigel
OL,10,FBlake, that he needed the salary for
OL,11,Fhis sick daughter, but Nigel replied,
OL,12,F"I don't care."
OL,14,FThe inquest heard there was a smoke
OL,15,Fdetector in the bedroom, and his fire
OL,16,Falarm was tested but was not in
OL,17,Fworking order.
OL,19,FThere was no carbon monoxide detector.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772110991
OL,3,CInquest hears farm worker's payments
OL,4,Cwere delayed before death
OL,6,FMr Castrudes posted a picture on
OL,7,Fsocial media showing the fire in a
OL,8,Fwashing machine drum on the decking
OL,9,Foutside his accommodation, alongside
OL,10,Femojis indicating how cold he was.
OL,12,FHis family also had concerns about the
OL,13,Fstandard of his accommodation and he
OL,14,Fhad told his sister Grace, due to late
OL,15,Fpayments he could not afford the
OL,16,Fbasics, such as heating and food.
OL,18,FGiving evidence in the inquest, his
OL,19,Fneighbour Nicola Bowley says on
OL,20,FSaturday, 18 January, the day before
OL,21,Fhis death, George knocked on her door.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772110991
OL,3,CInquest hears farm worker's payments
OL,4,Cwere delayed before death
OL,6,FNicola recalls George saying, "I need
OL,7,Fmoney, I have no food."
OL,9,FShe says she gave him soup and #10
OL,10,Fbefore telling George to talk to his
OL,11,Femployer, Nigel, but George explained
OL,12,Fhe had tried.
OL,14,FGeorge said that Nigel replied that it
OL,15,Fwas "not his problem."
OL,17,FShe says she did not remember hearing
OL,18,Fa fire alarm that night and described
OL,19,FGeorge as a "very smiley, cheerful
OL,20,Fman."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772110991
OL,3,CInquest hears farm worker's payments
OL,4,Cwere delayed before death
OL,6,FOn Saturday 18 January, George also
OL,7,Fcalled his family and mentioned that
OL,8,Fhe was having difficulty bearing the
OL,9,Fcold, and that he avoided using the
OL,10,Fheater because of the cost.
OL,12,FThe next day at 7:39pm, George was
OL,13,Frecovered by the fire service from
OL,14,Fwithin the cabin near the kitchen area.
OL,16,FAt 8:15pm, he was transferred to the
OL,17,Fintensive care unit, where he had
OL,18,Fsuffered a loss of brain function.
OL,20,FMr Castrudes died four days later.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772110991
OL,3,CInquest hears farm worker's payments
OL,4,Cwere delayed before death
OL,6,FCreating a working hypothesis, Watch
OL,7,FCommander Oliver Gleave believes the
OL,8,Fignition was caused by a cigarette
OL,9,Flighter, which ignited coal in a
OL,10,Fmakeshift fire pit.
OL,12,FHe says it was lit as a source of
OL,13,Fheating when temperatures were below
OL,14,Ffreezing outside.
OL,16,FHe added the fire started in a washing
OL,17,Fmachine drum placed in a hole in the
OL,18,Ffloor of the cabin, and within the
OL,19,Fdrum, there looked to be remnants of
OL,20,Fsmall pieces of charcoal.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772110991
OL,3,CInquest hears farm worker's payments
OL,4,Cwere delayed before death
OL,6,FCommander Gleave added that a half-
OL,7,Fempty bag of charcoal was on the
OL,8,Fdecking outside.
OL,10,FHe continued to explain that he thinks
OL,11,FMr Castrudes had been overcome by
OL,12,Fcarbon monoxide poisoning, suffering
OL,13,Ffrom dizziness and confusion, causing
OL,14,Fhim to collapse.
OL,16,FIt is thought his fall knocked the
OL,17,Ffire pit over, causing the fire to
OL,18,Fspread to the wooden flooring
OL,19,Funderneath the cabin.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
