OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1772110991
OL,3,CInquest hears farm worker's payments
OL,4,Cwere delayed before death
OL,6,FHe says the chipboard and insulation
OL,7,Fprovided fuel for the fire.
OL,9,FIt was also suggested by Advocate Matt
OL,10,FBerry, that his immigration status may
OL,11,Fhave also impacted his ability to
OL,12,Faddress any issues with his
OL,13,Faccommodation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/9
